---
import LayoutA from '../../layouts/LayoutA.astro';
---
<LayoutA title="Subtle Somatics — Earth & Flow" description="Presence-based coaching and spinal energetics with Kaja Possert-Bienzle.">

  <!-- Hero -->
  <section class="hero">
    <div class="hero-bg"><img src="/images/hero.jpg" alt="" /><div class="hero-overlay"></div></div>
    <div class="hero-content">
      <p class="hero-eyebrow">Subtle Somatics</p>
      <h1>Come home to the wisdom of your body</h1>
      <p class="hero-sub">Presence-based coaching and spinal energetics for those ready to meet themselves at the depth where transformation naturally unfolds.</p>
      <div class="hero-actions">
        <a href="#contact" class="btn">Book a Free Discovery Call</a>
        <a href="#services" class="btn btn-outline" style="border-color:var(--cream);color:var(--cream)">Explore Services</a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- About -->
  <section class="section" id="about">
    <div class="about-grid">
      <div class="about-image"><img src="/images/kaja-profile.jpg" alt="Kaja Possert-Bienzle" /></div>
      <div class="about-text">
        <p class="eyebrow">About Kaja</p>
        <h2>Unfolding companion. Wholeness witnesser. Integration facilitator.</h2>
        <p>I work with the natural intelligence of your body-mind-soul system — where sensations begin to speak, energy reorganises from the depth, and something deeply resonant in you starts moving through silent presence.</p>
        <p>This work is not about fixing or striving. It's about entering the field where what's true begins to reveal itself, in its own rhythm and time.</p>
        <p class="kaja-purpose"><em>"Container schaffen, in denen die nächsten Generationen gut begleitet werden können."</em></p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Philosophy -->
  <section class="philosophy">
    <div class="philosophy-inner">
      <h2 class="text-center">What if everything we need is already here?</h2>
      <p class="text-center philosophy-sub">Within each person lies a vast reservoir of innate resources — strength, courage, compassion, trust, and peace. These qualities are not something to be acquired from outside, but something to be uncovered, remembered, and embodied from within.</p>
      <div class="pillars">
        <div class="pillar">
          <div class="pillar-icon">
            <svg viewBox="0 0 40 40" width="40" height="40" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5"><circle cx="20" cy="20" r="15"/><circle cx="20" cy="20" r="6"/></svg>
          </div>
          <h3>An encounter</h3>
          <p>Truly getting to know the thoughts, emotions and sensations you have moment to moment.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="pillar">
          <div class="pillar-icon">
            <svg viewBox="0 0 40 40" width="40" height="40" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5"><path d="M20 5 C15 12, 12 18, 12 24 C12 30, 16 35, 20 35 C24 35, 28 30, 28 24 C28 18, 25 12, 20 5Z"/></svg>
          </div>
          <h3>An unfolding</h3>
          <p>Experiencing your vast inner resourcefulness — in the form of strength, love, presence and more.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="pillar">
          <div class="pillar-icon">
            <svg viewBox="0 0 40 40" width="40" height="40" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5"><path d="M8 20 Q14 8, 20 20 Q26 32, 32 20"/><path d="M8 20 Q14 32, 20 20 Q26 8, 32 20"/></svg>
          </div>
          <h3>An integration</h3>
          <p>Connecting into deeper coherence, alignment and embodiment of your innate wholeness.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Services -->
  <section class="section" id="services">
    <p class="eyebrow text-center">Services</p>
    <h2 class="text-center" style="margin-bottom:3rem">Two pathways, one intention</h2>
    <div class="services-grid">
      <div class="service-card">
        <div class="service-img"><img src="/images/subtle-coaching.png" alt="Subtle Coaching" /></div>
        <div class="service-body">
          <h3>Subtle Coaching</h3>
          <p>Meet yourself where you are in life right now — at the depth where you are vastly resourced to be with life's complexity.</p>
          <p>Through deepening self-contact and gentle inquiry, you begin to encounter the vast resources beneath the surface of habitual patterns. This is not talk therapy — it's an experiential exploration of what is present right now.</p>
          <ul>
            <li>Deepen connection to the present moment</li>
            <li>Access innate qualities of strength, love, and presence</li>
            <li>Cultivate self-contact and inner resourcefulness</li>
          </ul>
          <a href="#contact" class="btn btn-outline">Learn more</a>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="service-card">
        <div class="service-img"><img src="/images/spinal-energetics.png" alt="Spinal Energetics" /></div>
        <div class="service-body">
          <h3>Spinal Energetics</h3>
          <p>Experience profound mind-body-soul connection and integration — supported by subtle-and-powerful touch and sound.</p>
          <p>Working with the spine as a gateway to your energetic, emotional, and physical layers. The body's own intelligence is invited to reorganise, release, and integrate — in its own rhythm.</p>
          <ul>
            <li>Release stored tension and emotional patterns</li>
            <li>Reconnect with your body's natural intelligence</li>
            <li>Cultivate inner warmth, balance, and aliveness</li>
          </ul>
          <a href="#contact" class="btn btn-outline">Learn more</a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Expect -->
  <section class="expect">
    <div class="expect-inner">
      <h2>What to expect</h2>
      <div class="expect-grid">
        <div class="expect-item">
          <span class="expect-num">01</span>
          <h4>Discovery Call</h4>
          <p>A free conversation to sense into whether this work resonates. I'll listen to what's alive for you, and together we'll feel into the right next step.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="expect-item">
          <span class="expect-num">02</span>
          <h4>Your Session</h4>
          <p>Each session meets you exactly where you are. Whether coaching, spinal energetics, or both — the body leads, and I follow. Sessions run 60–75 minutes.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="expect-item">
          <span class="expect-num">03</span>
          <h4>Integration</h4>
          <p>Deeper transformation unfolds over time. Allow yourself space after each session. A series of sessions supports sustained embodiment of your wholeness.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Values -->
  <section class="section">
    <div class="values-grid">
      <div class="value"><h3>Presence</h3><p>Being fully here — with what is. Not fixing, not striving, but meeting the moment with open awareness.</p></div>
      <div class="value"><h3>Wholeness</h3><p>Recognising that you are already whole. Our work is about removing the layers that obscure this truth.</p></div>
      <div class="value"><h3>Embodiment</h3><p>Living from the body's wisdom. True knowing happens in the tissues, the breath, the bones.</p></div>
      <div class="value"><h3>Trust</h3><p>Trusting the rhythm of your own unfolding. There is an intelligence at work in you that knows the way.</p></div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Image Break -->
  <section class="image-break"><img src="/images/kaja-secondary.png" alt="Kaja in presence" /><div class="ib-overlay"></div></section>

  <!-- Contact -->
  <section class="section" id="contact">
    <div class="contact-grid">
      <div class="contact-text">
        <p class="eyebrow">Get in Touch</p>
        <h2>Ready to begin?</h2>
        <p>Whether you have questions, want to book a session, or simply feel drawn to connect — I'm here.</p>
        <p><strong>Email:</strong> <a href="mailto:connect@subtlesomatics.space">connect@subtlesomatics.space</a></p>
        <p><strong>Sessions:</strong> Online and in person</p>
        <p><strong>Based in:</strong> Austria (Vienna / Styria)</p>
      </div>
      <form class="contact-form" action="#">
        <input type="text" placeholder="Your name" />
        <input type="email" placeholder="Your email *" required />
        <textarea rows="5" placeholder="What's alive for you right now?" required></textarea>
        <button type="submit" class="btn">Send Message</button>
      </form>
    </div>
  </section>
</LayoutA>

<style>
  .hero { position: relative; min-height: 100vh; display: flex; align-items: center; overflow: hidden; }
  .hero-bg { position: absolute; inset: 0; }
  .hero-bg img { width: 100%; height: 100%; object-fit: cover; }
  .hero-overlay { position: absolute; inset: 0; background: linear-gradient(135deg, rgba(42,37,32,0.6) 0%, rgba(92,107,78,0.4) 50%, rgba(42,37,32,0.7) 100%); }
  .hero-content { position: relative; z-index: 1; max-width: 700px; padding: 2rem; margin-left: 8%; margin-top: 4rem; color: var(--cream); }
  .hero-eyebrow { font-family: var(--font-body); font-size: 0.8rem; letter-spacing: 0.2em; text-transform: uppercase; color: var(--sage-light); margin-bottom: 1.5rem; }
  .hero h1 { color: var(--cream); margin-bottom: 1.5rem; font-size: clamp(2.2rem, 5vw, 3.5rem); }
  .hero-sub { font-size: 1.1rem; line-height: 1.7; color: rgba(250,246,241,0.85); margin-bottom: 2.5rem; max-width: 550px; }
  .hero-actions { display: flex; gap: 1rem; flex-wrap: wrap; }

  .eyebrow { font-family: var(--font-body); font-size: 0.75rem; letter-spacing: 0.2em; text-transform: uppercase; color: var(--sage); margin-bottom: 0.8rem; }
  .about-grid { display: grid; grid-template-columns: 1fr 1.4fr; gap: 4rem; align-items: center; }
  .about-image img { border-radius: 2px; box-shadow: 0 20px 60px rgba(42,37,32,0.12); }
  .about-text h2 { margin-bottom: 1.5rem; font-size: clamp(1.6rem, 3vw, 2.2rem); line-height: 1.3; }
  .about-text p { margin-bottom: 1.2rem; }
  .kaja-purpose { color: var(--sage-dark); font-size: 0.95rem; margin-top: 1rem; }

  .philosophy { background: var(--sage-dark); color: var(--cream); padding: 6rem 2rem; }
  .philosophy-inner { max-width: 1100px; margin: 0 auto; }
  .philosophy h2 { color: var(--cream); margin-bottom: 1.5rem; font-style: italic; }
  .philosophy-sub { color: rgba(250,246,241,0.8); max-width: 650px; margin: 0 auto 4rem; }
  .pillars { display: grid; grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr); gap: 3rem; }
  .pillar { text-align: center; padding: 1.5rem; }
  .pillar-icon { color: var(--sage-light); margin-bottom: 1.5rem; display: flex; justify-content: center; }
  .pillar h3 { color: var(--sand-light); font-style: italic; margin-bottom: 1rem; }
  .pillar p { color: rgba(250,246,241,0.75); margin: 0 auto; font-size: 0.95rem; }

  .services-grid { display: grid; grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr; gap: 2.5rem; }
  .service-card { background: var(--white); border-radius: 2px; overflow: hidden; box-shadow: 0 4px 20px rgba(42,37,32,0.06); transition: transform 0.3s, box-shadow 0.3s; }
  .service-card:hover { transform: translateY(-4px); box-shadow: 0 12px 40px rgba(42,37,32,0.1); }
  .service-img img { width: 100%; height: 240px; object-fit: cover; }
  .service-body { padding: 2rem; }
  .service-body h3 { margin-bottom: 1rem; }
  .service-body p { margin-bottom: 1rem; font-size: 0.95rem; }
  .service-body ul { list-style: none; margin: 1.2rem 0 1.5rem; padding: 0; }
  .service-body li { padding: 0.4rem 0 0.4rem 1.5rem; position: relative; font-size: 0.9rem; color: var(--text-light); }
  .service-body li::before { content: '—'; position: absolute; left: 0; color: var(--sage); }

  .expect { background: var(--sand-light); padding: 6rem 2rem; }
  .expect-inner { max-width: 1100px; margin: 0 auto; }
  .expect h2 { margin-bottom: 3rem; }
  .expect-grid { display: grid; grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr); gap: 3rem; }
  .expect-item { padding: 1.5rem 0; }
  .expect-num { font-family: var(--font-heading); font-size: 2rem; color: var(--sage-light); display: block; margin-bottom: 1rem; }
  .expect-item h4 { font-family: var(--font-heading); font-size: 1.3rem; margin-bottom: 0.8rem; color: var(--warm-brown); }
  .expect-item p { font-size: 0.95rem; color: var(--text-light); }

  .values-grid { display: grid; grid-template-columns: repeat(2, 1fr); gap: 2.5rem; }
  .value { padding: 2rem; border-left: 3px solid var(--sage-light); }
  .value h3 { font-style: italic; color: var(--sage-dark); margin-bottom: 0.8rem; }
  .value p { font-size: 0.95rem; color: var(--text-light); }

  .image-break { position: relative; height: 50vh; overflow: hidden; }
  .image-break img { width: 100%; height: 100%; object-fit: cover; }
  .ib-overlay { position: absolute; inset: 0; background: linear-gradient(to bottom, rgba(42,37,32,0.05), rgba(42,37,32,0.15)); }

  .contact-grid { display: grid; grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr; gap: 4rem; align-items: start; }
  .contact-text h2 { margin-bottom: 1rem; }
  .contact-text p { margin-bottom: 0.8rem; }
  .contact-form { display: flex; flex-direction: column; gap: 1rem; }
  .contact-form input, .contact-form textarea { padding: 0.85rem 1rem; border: 1px solid var(--sand-dark); background: var(--white); font-family: var(--font-body); font-size: 0.95rem; color: var(--text); border-radius: 0; }
  .contact-form input:focus, .contact-form textarea:focus { outline: none; border-color: var(--sage); }
  .contact-form textarea { resize: vertical; min-height: 100px; }

  @media (max-width: 768px) {
    .hero-content { margin-left: 0; }
    .about-grid, .services-grid, .pillars, .expect-grid, .values-grid, .contact-grid { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
    .image-break { height: 35vh; }
  }
</style>
